<h4>https://www.apartments.com/pine-village-apartments-las-vegas-nv/7fysdny/ </h4>
At Pine Village Apartments we have 32 newly renovated 2 bedroom 1 bath apartments. These homes are fitted with brand new plank flooring and plush carpeting. The kitchen includes brand new cabinets, quartz countertops, and a stainless steel sink with a gooseneck faucet. Our remodeled bathrooms feature a new bathtub, cabinets and light fixtures. From the oven to the windows, everything is brand new!
Each apartment comes with a gas stove, refrigerator, and garbage disposal. Spend a relaxing afternoon in the community courtyard. Upper corner apartments include a balcony, perfect for hosting friends. Create your ideal environment with central heating and air.
Our affordable complex is conveniently located near The Las Vegas Strip, Meadows Mall, Clark High School, and the College of Southern Nevada.
